        {
            "title": "日本央行維持利率不變 密切關注近期加息行動影響",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 日本央行維持基準利率不變，繼續觀察上月加息對經濟的影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行周五宣布維持政策利率在0.75%，符合所有受訪經濟學家的預期。這使得借貸成本維持在三十年來的最高水平。政策聲明稱，央行將密切關注這對價格和經濟的影響，同時權衡下次行動的時機。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">央行行長植田和男將在晚些時候的新聞發布會上闡述本次政策決定背後的考量、利率可能的走向以及對通膨前景的看法。發布會通常於當地時間15:30開始。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他的表態可能會影響日圓匯率，他對最近長期殖利率飆升的任何評論也將受到市場密切關注。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-621e604e-513a-37eb-a9e9-1f4b29909a9e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題BOJ Keeps Rates Steady as It Monitors Impact of Recent Hike</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%8A-%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E5%8A%A0%E6%81%AF%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-031542993.html",
