            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "米萊為阿根廷對華貿易辯護 稱中國是很好的夥伴",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_.hiZ0nH7nWRipjNwHhuVg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3dcf8622bb96def98caf131730ddd3de\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 阿根廷總統哈維爾·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:米萊;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/米萊\">米萊</a>為該國日益加深的對華經貿關係辯護，稱阿根廷別無選擇，只能與北京開展貿易—同時尋求與美國達成協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周四在達沃斯世界經濟論壇期間接受彭博總編輯John Micklethwait採訪時，米萊巧妙地在意識形態上表達對美國總統特朗普政府的支持，同時在經濟層面向中國示好，並為自由貿易辯護。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「在我們看來，中國是一個很好的貿易夥伴，」米萊說。「如果你看看中國在全球的分量，就會明白我必須與中國開展貿易。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5f4fd2e1-e281-393e-8e11-9af0353fdff7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作為特朗普在地緣政治層面最親密的盟友之一，米萊試圖在華盛頓與北京之間保持微妙平衡。他在就任總統後措辭明顯趨於緩和，既未全然擁抱這一亞洲大國，也未將其徹底拒之門外。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿根廷2025年對中國的出口同比成長62%，增速遠快於同期對美國出口27%的增幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自特朗普重返白宮以來一直推動與美國達成自由貿易協定的米萊表示，「很快」就會就該協議傳來好消息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我的計畫是向歐盟開放、向美國開放，向中國開放，」米萊表示。「我想要開放的經濟。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Milei at Davos Hails Argentina’s China Ties in Defense of Trade</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B1%B3%E8%90%8A%E7%82%BA%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E5%B0%8D%E8%8F%AF%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E8%BE%AF%E8%AD%B7-%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%AF%E5%BE%88%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A5%E4%BC%B4-142856162.html",
